{"title":"人民日报周年纪念祝词","authors":["刘子久"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":5,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民日报周年纪念祝词"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘子久"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民日报创刊后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月十五是周年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报社发起来纪念，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"征求读者的意见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"批评建议须内行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办报俺是门外汉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今都兴说快板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺也来向有才大哥学一番。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各种精神食粮内，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报纸要占第一端。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发行多，传播远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大小村庄都普遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消息灵，故事鲜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天出版不问断。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"印刷清，文字浅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"识字男女都能看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邮费低，定价廉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花钱不多真方便。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天看报成习惯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不看就像没吃饭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报纸好处说不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的作用更显然。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能教育，能宣传，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组织领导非等闲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣传教育的政策，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也在这里提一番："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣传教育的目的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加强团结与斗志。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我人民解放区，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"样样都是光明的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若有个别的缺点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是美中的不足。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若拿优点比缺点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似沧海之一粟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬拿一粟作论题，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是吹毛去求疵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在人民的缺点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都应归罪蒋介石。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌颂暴露何所择？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席早已有指示。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌颂意义是鼓励，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴露目的是打击。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人应该受打击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农应该受鼓励。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应该鼓励的反打击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人一定笑嘻嘻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人为何笑嘻嘻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑我自己骂自己。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说这话你不信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“野百合花”有前例。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民缺点如何办，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说服启发去教育。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等他自己觉悟了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自我批评更有益。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都喜欢上进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁甘自暴与自弃？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"优点大胆去表扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缺点相形易革去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种方式为甚好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着好的去看齐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣传教育些什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有理有利与有力："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有理就是讲政策，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有利好比分土地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各种革命斗争中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有力才能够胜利。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说话还须有节制，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保证言行要齐一。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有那些法西斯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃饭专靠吹牛皮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报在组织领导上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等于许多巡视团。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传达上级的指示，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号称喉舌不虚传。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反映下面的意见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同玻璃镜一般。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个运动决定后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号召宣传它承担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等到人人懂得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会搞得热火朝天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"典型介绍效果大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"示范作用不平凡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吸收总结传经验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干群进步有根源。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各种劳模上了报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个好比中状元。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越鼓励来越加油，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推动工作更向前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种办法谁提倡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席来告诉咱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报纸内容何为主，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因时因地有变换；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当前中心三件事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打仗翻身和生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是单说这三件，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻重缓急不一般。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平均主义不能犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经常应该有重点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报纸必须大众化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农才能解得下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民生活要熟悉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民语言要通达。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熟悉才能不外行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通达运用才熟练。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字要熟，句要短，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"标点符号要简单。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老幼能听懂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能深入到民间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众路线怎搞起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还得请示毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“从群众中来，到去群众中”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领会运用要彻底。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“从来”全凭通讯网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“到去”依靠邮政局。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好坏以何为标准？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级立场是第一。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内容形式何为主，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术服务于政治。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想放毒要警惕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麻木不仁要不的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想把报纸办得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许多问题要注意："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新闻固须要审查，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社论更要“开机器”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内容当然要讨论，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文字也须加考虑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下笔千言有毛病，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自以为是要不的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各种稿件草完后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"增减删改是必须。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是标题与排版，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"样样都不能儿戏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地位前后字大小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表示轻重与缓急。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"印刷技术要提高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"模糊不清误大事。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"校对人员须仔细，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"错漏颠倒犯纪律。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论文章和消息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要联系理论与实际。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首长应当要负责，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲自动眼又动笔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种规矩谁建立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马恩列斯毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党报要想办得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的的确确不容易。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全党负责还不够，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必须人民齐出力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民力量无限大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前途光明有出息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民日报是人民的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了人民谋利益。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诌到这里就打住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"略表庆贺祝努力。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}